&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Newton ward PICU is a Psychiatric Intensive Care unit based at the Clock View Hospital site in Walton&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are currently 12 bedded mixed sex PICU serving the residents of both North and South Liverpool&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking to recruit band 5 staff nurses who would bring a caring and professional attitude to work with a service user group who require a high level of support.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The PICU cares for services users with a high level of acuity and the role requires commitment, experience and a positive attitude toward working as part of a team&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Candidates should be compassionate, enthusiastic and motivated to work in a fast pace acute environment&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Previous experience within a Mental Health care setting is preferable&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Candidate should have full NMC registration and experience of working with individuals who have mental health needs is essential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Shortlisting is planned for 9th November 2020.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Interviews are planned for 17th November 2020.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
